name: FORMATIONS #11
description:
Realtime, generative app. 

Memo Akten (memo.tv); originally created sometime in the 90s using C; ported to Processing (Java) in 2006; ported to p5js (JavaScript) and minted in 2021 for #sketch4processing fundraiser. All primary sales during the fundraiser (20-22 Aug 2021) will go to the Processing Foundation. 

Refresh or double-click/tap the screen to create a brand new FORMATION (also happens automatically every 5 minutes).
